gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Thunder 127, Spurs 89
gameRecap.excerpt: Oklahoma City defeats San Antonio, 127-89. For Oklahoma City, Shai Gilgeous-Alexander led the way with 26 points, six rebounds, and five assists while aided by Josh Giddey (20 points, 12 rebounds, seven assists) in the victory. Zach Collins finished with 20 points, seven rebounds, and two blocks for San Antonio in the losing effort. Oklahoma City improves to 55-25, while San Antonio moves to 20-60 with the loss.
